               <p>WILLIAM BAILEY. I am a <rs id="t18170917-248-viclabel1265" type="occupation">smith</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-248-victim1706 t18170917-248-viclabel1265"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18170917-248-crimeloc1266">Brick-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18170917-248-crimeloc1266" type="placeName" value="Brick-lane"></interp>
