                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-248-off1263 t18170917-248-crimeloc1266"></join>. On the 3d of September, about half-past twelve o'clock at night, I met the prisoner; she stopped me, took my watch from me, and ran away.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170917-248-person1707">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BROWN
               <interp inst="t18170917-248-person1707" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
