                     <interp inst="t18170917-248-person1707" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I saw the prisoner running and the prosecutor following her. I found her laying in a cart. She acknowledged she had the watch, and gave it to me.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
